Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.54,0:00:06.06,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Menma didn't disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.51,0:00:09.26,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Even after the firework had ended,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.00,0:00:13.14,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Menma hadn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.94,0:00:19.16,Default,All,0,0,0,,Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.15,0:00:23.79,Default,Bro,0,0,0,,The firework was amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.10,0:00:27.03,Default,Bro,0,0,0,,Thank you for inviting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.03,0:00:28.26,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.26,0:00:34.18,Default,Bro,0,0,0,,And thank you also for doing all this for my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.74,0:00:36.12,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Saa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.02,0:00:44.00,Default,Bro,0,0,0,,I've got to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.00,0:00:45.80,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,All right. Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.09,0:00:48.23,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.15,0:00:48.25,Default,Bro,0,0,0,,What? You came to get me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.48,0:00:50.61,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.46,0:00:56.86,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,We should go too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.86,0:00:57.49,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.17,0:01:02.47,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,For Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.59,0:01:05.16,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,That's a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.02,0:01:09.16,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,I guess I had some other wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.71,0:01:11.49,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.55,0:01:15.67,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,But actually, I'm a little glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.67,0:01:19.81,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Because they've been playing "Dodosuko" a lot on TV lately, which I really like. {dodosuko is the name of a song; people can look it up on youtube}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.81,0:01:20.41,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.41,0:01:23.82,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Do you know what "Dodosuko" is, Jintan?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.47,0:01:23.83,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,The reason Menma didn't go to heaven...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.84,0:01:25.19,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,...really tries hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.19,0:01:28.69,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,...wasn't because she had another wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.38,0:01:33.86,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Could it have been...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.55,0:01:41.10,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Hey, if you're going to sleep do it upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.90,0:01:48.92,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Hello? Yukiatsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.80,0:01:51.39,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Menma's asleep right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.39,0:01:54.57,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Then come out right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.57,0:01:56.55,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Make sure Menma doesn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.55,0:01:57.50,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.81,0:02:04.22,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Uhh... what exactly is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.74,0:02:07.79,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Why do you think Menma didn't go to heaven?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.79,0:02:08.81,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.81,0:02:13.51,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,Is it because the firework wasn't Menma's real wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.51,0:02:14.40,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.15,0:02:19.95,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,The reason Menma didn't go to heaven isn't that she had another wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.45,0:02:24.68,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,Hey, were we really looking out for Menma?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.68,0:02:28.25,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,Were we really hoping that her wish would be granted?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:31.89,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,I know that I was only thinking about myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.60,0:02:36.96,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,Because I didn't want to keep seeing Jintan knowing he was thinking about Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.80,0:02:40.83,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,I wanted her to go to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.83,0:02:44.10,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,I didn't care about granting her wish,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:47.74,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,I wanted her to go to heaven for my sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.74,0:02:51.21,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,God must have seen through me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.21,0:02:52.09,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,It's the same with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.08,0:02:55.80,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,I love Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.39,0:02:58.76,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Time has passed since then,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.76,0:03:02.14,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,but it shocks even me how my love for her hasn't changed a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.94,0:03:06.64,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,But now, only Yadomi could see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.16,0:03:11.16,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,I couldn't bear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.39,0:03:16.53,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Jintan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:26.19,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.52,0:03:30.30,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,I could stand her being Yadomi's alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.30,0:03:34.44,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,So I thought that granting her wish and having her go to heaven would be easier for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.44,0:03:36.08,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,You're the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.08,0:03:37.70,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Yeah, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.70,0:03:39.60,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,You're terrible too, Tsuruko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.60,0:03:43.58,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,Stop hiding your feelings. Don't you have something to tell Yukiatsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.58,0:03:44.66,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:45.49,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Tsurumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:46.64,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,It's the same as last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.19,0:03:51.15,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,That day you two plotted together
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.15,0:03:53.66,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,to test Menma's feelings for Jintan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.30,0:03:55.81,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.81,0:03:59.80,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,I know, I've always envied Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:01.75,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,But you're exactly the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.75,0:04:02.83,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,No I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.83,0:04:03.51,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,Yes you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.51,0:04:09.08,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,You're envious of Menma because you love Yukiatsu, so you tried to make her go to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.86,0:04:10.60,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:11.68,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.66,0:04:15.81,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,I'm not envious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.81,0:04:20.48,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,I've always known I couldn't measure up to Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:24.93,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,I'm not like you. I don't dream about things that can't come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.93,0:04:25.34,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.34,0:04:26.64,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,I've already told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.64,0:04:30.36,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,Even if Menma goes to heaven, you're the replacement.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.36,0:04:31.11,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.11,0:04:33.19,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,I didn't mind being a replacement.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.57,0:04:38.56,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,The one I've always been envious of since back then is you, Anaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.34,0:04:44.40,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,Now, just like back then, you're Yukiatsu's confidant. That hurts me so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.78,0:04:49.66,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,That's why I tattled on you that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.64,0:04:54.64,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,I told Menma that you were going to test Jintan's feelings for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.37,0:04:56.80,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Menma knew about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.80,0:04:59.82,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Then why didn't she say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:01.64,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,Menma said...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.42,0:05:05.67,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Hmm, I wonder what I should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.67,0:05:10.43,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,What do you mean you wonder? Those two called Jintan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.43,0:05:12.73,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,They said not to tell you about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:16.34,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,Isn't that mean? Let's go tell them we're angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.61,0:05:23.79,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,But I really like everyone, not just Jintan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:29.76,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,That's when I knew I couldn't measure up to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.62,0:05:37.00,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,It took a long time, but I finally became Yukiatsu's confidant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:40.09,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,I was satisfied with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:44.27,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,But now I know that even now the one by Yukiatsu's side is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.27,0:05:45.55,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Tsuruko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.23,0:05:50.99,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,I thought that if Menma went to heaven Anaru would cling to Jintan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:53.99,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,If that happened, I'd have my place back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.99,0:05:57.45,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm terrible. I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.45,0:06:01.34,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,So it was impossible after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.73,0:06:06.50,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,How could we send Menma to heaven when we feel this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.73,0:06:08.33,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,What's it matter how you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.33,0:06:11.61,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,It's a lot better than not doing anything at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.05,0:06:15.09,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,What's wrong Poppo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.09,0:06:17.94,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,If I don't grant Menma's wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:21.08,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,If I don't make her go to heaven...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.06,0:06:25.98,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,If I don't, Menma will never forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.09,0:06:30.15,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Poppo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.15,0:06:31.96,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:37.71,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,On that day, I saw Menma pass away...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.17,0:06:41.73,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,I was scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.34,0:06:45.09,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,I was afraid of staying here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.09,0:06:49.82,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,I wanted to run away, but for some reason I couldn't get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.82,0:06:52.14,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,I'm living in the base we built together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:57.68,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,I didn't go to school. I thought that if I went somewhere far away in the world, things would change.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.68,0:06:58.53,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.94,0:07:03.78,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,But I always return to that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.35,0:07:05.77,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,I'm begging you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.89,0:07:12.42,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,I'm begging you, please make Menma go to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:14.62,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,I know it's selfish of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.00,0:07:19.55,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,It might be impossible to make Menma go to heaven when I feel this way, but I can't let it go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.40,0:07:29.30,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,I can't let go of the sight of Menma slowly, steadily drifting further away from me that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.78,0:07:37.68,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,I wasn't the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.24,0:07:42.76,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Everyone wanted Menma to go to heaven for their own sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.42,0:07:46.72,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,We weren't serious about granting Menma's wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.03,0:07:51.10,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:54.36,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:58.03,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,How about now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.03,0:08:00.40,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.89,0:08:04.10,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.10,0:08:05.17,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:07.07,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.07,0:08:11.74,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Oh? Jintan's not home? I wonder if he's still at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.74,0:08:13.35,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Geez, he left all the lights on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.35,0:08:14.49,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.12,0:08:16.93,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I'm home, Touko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.93,0:08:22.22,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Jintan spent this afternoon with everyone from the Super Peace Busters.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.22,0:08:26.60,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Jintan's been acting a lot more energetic, lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.12,0:08:29.70,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I guess I'll go take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.70,0:08:34.27,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Jintan's been... Lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.35,0:08:38.95,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.91,0:08:41.54,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,Apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.11,0:08:43.80,Default,All,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.80,0:08:46.15,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,I don't care about Jintan anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.15,0:08:49.24,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,I'm going to apologize to Menma. That way...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.24,0:08:49.70,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Anaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.70,0:08:50.76,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.76,0:08:53.21,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,You have two sets of eyelashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.95,0:08:55.52,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,Oh no! My fake lashes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.64,0:08:58.60,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,Hey, Yukiatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.60,0:09:02.25,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,I'd thought the way your eyes looked had changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:03.60,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,Tsuruko, not you too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.60,0:09:08.01,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,You're so hairy already Anaru, why would you want to add any more?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.01,0:09:10.29,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Anaru's fine the way she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.08,0:09:13.05,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.05,0:09:15.45,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,But don't keep calling me Anaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.65,0:09:17.83,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.83,0:09:20.19,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,We've all switched to using our nicknames again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.19,0:09:21.30,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.15,0:09:31.55,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Yukiatsu was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.55,0:09:32.45,Default,All,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.45,0:09:36.82,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Somewhere deep inside, I was happy that I was the only one who could see Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.82,0:09:37.74,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Jintan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.74,0:09:40.56,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,But Menma's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.20,0:09:45.31,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,To be honest, I didn't care about sending her off to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.40,0:09:48.85,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,But she didn't feel that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.33,0:09:53.54,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,She said she wanted to speak normally with everyone, not just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.54,0:09:55.69,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,That's why she wanted to go to heaven and be reincarnated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.10,0:10:01.76,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Let's really grant Menma's wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:06.50,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Let's call Menma and communicate with her properly using her diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.95,0:10:10.00,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Let's try it one more time, together with Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:13.71,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,Yeah. There's no point in talking about it without Menma here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:14.64,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,After all...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.64,0:10:19.25,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,There're six of us in the Super Peace Busters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.25,0:10:19.92,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.92,0:10:21.70,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,Hey, that's my line!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.31,0:10:27.37,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.68,0:10:33.11,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'll bring Menma right away. Let's meet at the secret base.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:42.78,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Menma... It finally feels like we've started moving again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.88,0:10:45.54,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,We'll grant your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.10,0:10:50.70,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,And this time for sure, we'll proudly send you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.70,0:10:51.69,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Menma!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.84,0:10:58.98,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,M...Menma?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:03.18,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.27,0:11:08.90,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Hey Menma! What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.90,0:11:09.99,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Why are you like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.99,0:11:14.78,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,It looks like my wish already came true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.83,0:11:21.97,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,I remembered the promise I made with your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:24.23,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,With my mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.74,0:11:28.50,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,There's just one thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:29.24,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.24,0:11:31.11,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Jintan won't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:36.95,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,I think he's been forcing himself to act strong ever since I got sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.95,0:11:38.47,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Auntie?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.47,0:11:43.27,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to being reincarnated, but that's the one thing that worries me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.36,0:11:46.85,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,I've made him put up with a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.85,0:11:54.09,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,I really wanted him to laugh, get mad, and cry more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:56.01,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.07,0:12:00.54,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,I promise you I'll definitely make Jintan cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.38,0:12:08.50,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Thank you Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.20,0:12:12.30,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,I'll be counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.96,0:12:15.00,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.20,0:12:21.66,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,And even though I thought about it a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.66,0:12:26.26,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,I just couldn't figure out what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.26,0:12:31.52,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,That's why I decided to ask everyone for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.25,0:12:37.69,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,So I called everyone and asked them to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:41.19,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,But it's not like I wanted to get everyone together to bully you or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.36,0:12:37.71,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,The wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.19,0:12:43.15,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,It's just that I'm not very smart...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.85,0:12:41.20,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,That Menma wanted to be granted so badly...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:46.86,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,...think of a way to make you cry without bullying...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:45.41,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,That she returned here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.15,0:12:52.15,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,But it didn't work out at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:58.62,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,I wonder if that was a punishment for keeping it secret from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.62,0:13:00.70,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,It's not some punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.70,0:13:02.14,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,I just go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.14,0:13:03.62,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter if you keep it a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.58,0:13:09.26,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,I always go there, even if I don't have a reason to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:14.17,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,You're crying again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.90,0:13:21.56,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,But to be honest, I like it more when you laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.13,0:13:26.90,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,I guess it's about time to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.87,0:13:28.74,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.74,0:13:30.27,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,You can't go yet, please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.50,0:13:31.10,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.50,0:13:33.00,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,I can't be the only one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.00,0:13:33.65,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.71,0:13:38.11,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,I've wanted to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:40.61,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,All this time, I've wanted to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.61,0:13:43.26,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,I've wanted to call out your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.26,0:13:45.10,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,I've wanted to apologize to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.70,0:13:47.09,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,I've wanted to tell you I loved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.09,0:13:48.05,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Jintan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.05,0:13:53.47,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,But everyone else feels the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.47,0:13:56.28,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,They all love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.28,0:13:57.90,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,They all wanted to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:13:59.60,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Everyone's waiting for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.94,0:14:02.59,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Over at our place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.71,0:14:17.54,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Menma...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:19.37,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Jintan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.37,0:14:22.08,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,I wanted to grant your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.08,0:14:23.81,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,I love you so much, Jintan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.81,0:14:26.34,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,But this is so sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.34,0:14:29.00,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,I had fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.00,0:14:31.52,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,I want to be with you forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.52,0:14:37.50,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,So much that I've thought it would be nice to stay like this with you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.93,0:14:40.67,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,J...Jintan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.77,0:14:45.36,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:48.50,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Ji...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.50,0:14:51.19,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Menma. Menma? Menma!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.19,0:14:52.19,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,What is it, Jintan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.88,0:14:54.16,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.16,0:14:55.04,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.04,0:14:56.70,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,Has Menma...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.70,0:14:57.94,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.94,0:14:59.66,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Jintan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.66,0:15:03.10,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Menma! What's going on? Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.10,0:15:05.17,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Hurry up and come out! Menma!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.17,0:15:07.41,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Menma. Menma!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.41,0:15:08.22,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,Hey, Jintan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:09.15,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Menma!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.15,0:15:10.02,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.02,0:15:11.04,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Menma!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.04,0:15:14.35,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,It... it's hide and seek.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.27,0:15:18.27,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,What do you mean, hide and seek?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.27,0:15:19.11,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Jintan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.11,0:15:20.08,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Hey Menma!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.08,0:15:21.62,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Is Menma playing hide and seek?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.62,0:15:22.71,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,Hide and seek?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:25.51,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Hey Jintan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.51,0:15:26.32,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.32,0:15:28.34,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Menma!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.34,0:15:29.57,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Let's all go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:30.33,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.33,0:15:30.81,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.81,0:15:31.48,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.41,0:15:38.50,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,No... Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.11,0:15:46.43,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,I still haven't said goodbye properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.43,0:15:48.45,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Menma!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.45,0:15:51.15,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,Menma!
