Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.18,0:15:58.72,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.42,0:15:59.99,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.24,0:15:59.99,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.24,0:16:02.07,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.03,0:16:04.28,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.44,0:16:04.27,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:09.23,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.23,0:16:11.08,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Just a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.90,0:16:17.33,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Just a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.57,0:16:28.38,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Jintan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:30.31,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Did you find Menma?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.24,0:16:32.65,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Your feet...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:37.22,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,Jintan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.30,0:16:41.05,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,So that means Menma is already...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.36,0:16:49.81,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.94,0:16:57.09,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,These are from the diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.09,0:16:59.09,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,This is Menma's writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.76,0:17:00.54,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.05,0:17:40.95,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,I made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.67,0:17:47.44,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,This time I managed to say goodbye properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.75,0:17:48.70,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Now I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.70,0:17:49.89,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.52,0:17:53.09,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,What's going on, Menma?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:54.92,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,This is hide and seek, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.58,0:18:01.38,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,That means it can't end until we find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.10,0:18:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Jintan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.72,0:18:07.36,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Are you ready yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.26,0:18:11.10,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Are you ready yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.65,0:18:16.13,Default,All,0,0,0,,Are you ready yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.13,0:18:18.95,Default,All,0,0,0,,Are you ready yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.43,0:18:22.86,Default,All,0,0,0,,Are you ready yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.86,0:18:26.28,Default,All,0,0,0,,Are you ready yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.28,0:18:28.85,Default,All,0,0,0,,Are you ready yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.85,0:18:31.76,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Now I'm ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.59,0:18:37.05,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,That was Menma's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.71,0:18:40.60,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,It can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.89,0:18:43.10,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Menma?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.25,0:18:45.01,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,Menma!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.37,0:18:49.71,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,Is that really Menma?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.10,0:18:52.61,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Menma. It's Menma!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.61,0:18:53.52,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,I can see her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.52,0:18:54.50,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,Menma!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.77,0:18:56.41,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Menma!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.41,0:18:57.99,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,I can see you, Menma!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.99,0:19:02.09,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.81,0:19:06.35,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,You're not supposed to just say my name now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.35,0:19:07.16,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.42,0:19:11.48,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,I'm really bad at hide and seek.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.48,0:19:14.47,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Come on Jintan, say what you're supposed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.88,0:19:16.46,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.46,0:19:20.36,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,That way it'll end the right way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.28,0:19:28.31,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,I read your letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.31,0:19:31.20,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,I really like you too, Menma!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.16,0:19:34.49,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,I really like you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.49,0:19:36.54,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,I really like you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.54,0:19:38.32,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,And of course I really like you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.95,0:19:46.92,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,A goodbye isn't supposed to be one-sided.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.92,0:19:48.88,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Right, Jintan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.40,0:19:57.69,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Thank you for granting that wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.69,0:19:59.86,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,I love you, Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.95,0:20:06.11,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,Hey! Jintan made Menma cry again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.11,0:20:07.14,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Jintan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.14,0:20:08.74,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,Why'd you do that Jintan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.74,0:20:09.62,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.62,0:20:14.55,Default,Popo,0,0,0,,Made her cry, made her cry. I'll tell the teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.55,0:20:16.19,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Poppo you traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.19,0:20:18.32,Default,Anaru,0,0,0,,Haven't you done enough yet, Jintan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.32,0:20:19.35,Default,Tsuru,0,0,0,,Jintan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.35,0:20:21.45,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Shut up, Poppo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.45,0:20:23.25,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Why's it my fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.48,0:20:30.92,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,I want to be with everyone longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.06,0:20:33.72,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,I want to play with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.64,0:20:38.59,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,That's why I'll be reborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.89,0:20:43.30,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,I'll be... together... with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.82,0:20:44.70,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.59,0:20:48.18,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,Jintan cried.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.91,0:20:50.85,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,I've said goodbye...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.75,0:20:53.05,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,So now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.61,0:20:58.77,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Ready, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.70,0:21:03.93,Default,All,0,0,0,,We found you, Menma!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.95,0:21:11.00,Default,Menma,0,0,0,,You found me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.90,0:21:16.83,Default,Jin,0,0,0,,Menma was smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.30,0:21:34.90,Default,Jin,0,0,100,,We're turning into adults.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.54,0:21:51.83,Default,Jin,0,0,100,,As the seasons turn,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.83,0:21:56.25,Default,Jin,0,0,100,,the flowers blooming by the side of the road also change.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.25,0:22:01.16,Default,Jin,0,0,100,,I wonder what the name of the flower that bloomed that season was.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.49,0:22:04.10,Default,Jin,0,0,100,,It swayed ever so slightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.95,0:22:07.50,Default,Jin,0,0,100,,If you touched it, it prickled.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.50,0:22:09.68,Default,Jin,0,0,100,,If you brought it to your nose,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.11,0:22:13.41,Default,Jin,0,0,100,,it gave off a scent of ripeness and sunshine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.60,0:22:18.97,Default,Jin,0,0,100,,That fragrance gradually dissipates.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.04,0:22:22.77,Default,Jin,0,0,100,,We're becoming adults.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.28,0:22:26.16,Default,Jin,0,0,100,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.11,0:22:33.37,Default,Jin,0,0,100,,That flower is definitely still blooming somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.35,0:22:44.77,Default,Jin,0,0,100,,Yeah. We'll keep on...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.82,0:22:49.79,Default,Jin,0,0,100,,...granting that flower's wish forever.
